text:
Sexy, modern, gorgeous, clean.

BF and I received a complimentary suite upgrade: 
-comfy, lush king bed; 
-spacious living room with kitchen sink, mini fridge (with room for personal items!), microwave, and dishwasher; 
-large closets with full length mirrors and a cushioned chest for sitting and even more storage; 
-private balcony with seating and an AMAZING view of the strip; 
-generously sized shower with a soaking tub roomy enough for two (or more!); 
-separate toilet with a door (so you can keep your stink in there);
-and two bathroom sinks with bright lighting to indulge yourself in narcissism (I only wish there were more counter space). 

Oh, and two TVs if you want to spend a day vegging out, ordering room service, and laying in bed all day like I did. I loved the look and feel of everything in (and out) of our room.

The Cosmo has its own casinos, a few lounges and bars (each with different vibes), as well as the infamous Marquee, so you don't have to venture far to have a jam-packed\/memorable night.

I loved our stay here and would absolutely come again!
